list.comment:
Added click-player-menu: true to config.yml if you want to open a menu when interacting with a player;
Added stats-duels: true to config.yml if you want to disable the duels statistics icon;
Added MatchMaking to MenuPreferences;
Added MatchMaking system (Currently only compatible with Duels and BedWars in future updates);
Improved error detection system;

Fixed an issue when trying to interact with another player and opening the stats menu;
Fixed a bug in the universal booster message;
Fixed translation errors in all languages;
Fixed the coin display in the profile menu stats;
Minor fixes to some methods.

